INSERT INTO `movie` VALUES (8,'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel primal male aggression into a shocking new form of therapy. Their concept catches on, with underground \"fight clubs\" forming in every town, until an eccentric gets in the way and ignites an out-of-control spiral toward oblivion.','Fight Club',_binary '',1999,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pB8BM7pdSp6B6Ih7QZ4DrQ3PmJK.jpg',1728172800000,550),(9,'Jack Torrance accepts a caretaker job at the Overlook Hotel, where he, along with his wife Wendy and their son Danny, must live isolated from the rest of the world for the winter. But they aren\'t prepared for the madness that lurks within.','The Shining',_binary '',1980,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xazWoLealQwEgqZ89MLZklLZD3k.jpg',1728259200000,694),(10,'A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster\'s moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.','Pulp Fiction',_binary '',1994,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg',1728345600000,680),(11,'Taking place after alien crafts land around the world, an expert linguist is recruited by the military to determine whether they come in peace or are a threat.','Arrival',_binary '',2016,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/x2FJsf1ElAgr63Y3PNPtJrcmpoe.jpg',1728432000000,329865),(12,'Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.','Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind',_binary '',2004,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5MwkWH9tYHv3mV9OdYTMR5qreIz.jpg',1728518400000,38),(13,'A man with a low IQ has accomplished great things in his life and been present during significant historic events—in each case, far exceeding what anyone imagined he could do. But despite all he has achieved, his one true love eludes him.','Forrest Gump',_binary '',1994,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/arw2vcBveWOVZr6pxd9XTd1TdQa.jpg',1728518400000,13),(14,'Held in an L.A. interrogation room, Verbal Kint attempts to convince the feds that a mythic crime lord, Keyser Soze, not only exists, but was also responsible for drawing him and his four partners into a multi-million dollar heist that ended with an explosion in San Pedro harbor – leaving few survivors. Verbal lures his interrogators with an incredible story of the crime lord\'s almost supernatural prowess.','The Usual Suspects',_binary '',1995,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rWbsxdwF9qQzpTPCLmDfVnVqTK1.jpg',1728864000000,629),(15,'Dr. Steven Murphy is a renowned cardiovascular surgeon who presides over a spotless household with his wife and two children. Lurking at the margins of his idyllic suburban existence is Martin, a fatherless teen who insinuates himself into the doctor\'s life in gradually unsettling ways.','The Killing of a Sacred Deer',_binary '',2017,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e4DGlsc9g0h5AyoyvvAuIRnofN7.jpg',1728864000000,399057),(16,'While on a trip to Paris with his fiancée\'s family, a nostalgic screenwriter finds himself mysteriously going back to the 1920s every day at midnight.','Midnight in Paris',_binary '',2011,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4wBG5kbfagTQclETblPRRGihk0I.jpg',1729036800000,59436),(17,'A teacher lives a lonely life, all the while struggling over his son’s custody. His life slowly gets better as he finds love and receives good news from his son, but his new luck is about to be brutally shattered by an innocent little lie.','The Hunt',_binary '',2012,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jkixsXzRh28q3PCqFoWcf7unghT.jpg',1729987200000,103663),(18,'Two homicide detectives are on a desperate hunt for a serial killer whose crimes are based on the \"seven deadly sins\" in this dark and haunting film that takes vi